Crystal Collector

Random number generated and presented to player

player has a choice of four Crystals each with a randomly generated hidden number assigned to them

New Random number generated every time after win or loss

Player clicks a crystal of their choice and this adds the random number generated assigned to the crystal

random crystal numbers are between 1 and 12

Must click on crystals w random hidden numbers until player hits the same random generated number

If you go over its a loss and game starts over

if you get equal to the computer choice its a win and game starts over.


